Entities
Strong: Customer, Product, Campaign
Weak: CustomerDependent
Assosicative: Customer Campaign

Relationships
One to One: Customer to contact profile
One to Many: Customer to Customer Dependent
Many to Many:  Customer to CustomerCampaign to Campaign

Attributes
Identifier: Customer: CustomerID, Product: ProductID, Campaign: CampaignID, CustomerDependent: (CustomerID, DependentID), CustomerCampaign: (CustomerID, CampaignID)
Mandatory: Customer: Year_Birth, Education, Marital_Status, Campaign: CampaignName, StartDate, CustomerCampaign: AcceptedFlag, Product: Name, Category
Optional: Customer: Income, Complain, CustomerDependent: DependentAge, CustomerCampaign: ResponseDate
Singlevalue:Year_Birth, Education, Income, Name, Category, DependentType, AcceptedFlag

